OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772447793
OL,3,CGrooming gang whistleblower taking
OL,4,CGovernment to court
OL,6,FA police whistleblower is taking the
OL,7,Fgovernment to court over claims it has
OL,8,Ffailed to implement recommendations to
OL,9,Fprotect children from sexual
OL,10,Fexploitation.
OL,12,FMaggie Oliver is bringing a judicial
OL,13,Freview to the High Court following the
OL,14,Foutcome of the Independent Inquiry
OL,15,Finto Child Sexual Abuse (IICSA).
OL,17,FThe inquiry, which took seven years
OL,18,Fand cost #200 million, was launched to
OL,19,Fexamine how public and private
OL,20,Finstitutions failed to protect
OL,21,Fchildren from sexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772447793
OL,3,CGrooming gang whistleblower taking
OL,4,CGovernment to court
OL,6,FChair Alexis Jay's final report, in
OL,7,F2022, recommended 20 major reforms to
OL,8,Fchild protection in England and Wales.
OL,10,FMs Oliver, who set up The Maggie
OL,11,FOliver Foundation after quitting
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police over the
OL,13,Fforce's inaction over grooming gangs,
OL,14,Fsaid despite repeated public
OL,15,Fcommitments, successive governments
OL,16,Fhave yet to implement many of the
OL,17,Fchild protection reforms recommended
OL,18,Fin the IICSA report.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772447793
OL,3,CGrooming gang whistleblower taking
OL,4,CGovernment to court
OL,6,FThe former detective said: "Survivors
OL,7,Fof child sexual abuse were promised
OL,8,Fchange. Instead, they are met with
OL,9,Fdelay after delay."
OL,11,FAuthorities still do not collect
OL,12,Fethnic and religious data on
OL,13,Fperpetrators of child abuse - key
OL,14,Frecommendations included in the report.
OL,16,FBaroness Louise Casey recently found a
OL,17,Fsignificant over-representation of
OL,18,FAsian men who are suspects in grooming
OL,19,Fgangs, adding though authorities are
OL,20,Fin "denial", more needs to be done to
OL,21,Funderstand why this is the case.
OL,26,@nD@\OU|D@DOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772447793
OL,3,CGrooming gang whistleblower taking
OL,4,CGovernment to court
OL,6,FOther recommendations still to be
OL,7,Fimplemented are ensuring children in
OL,8,Fcare have the same access to justice
OL,9,Fas others and ending the use of pain-
OL,10,Finducing restraint on children in
OL,11,Fcustody, a practice described in the
OL,12,FIICSA report as "amounting to torture".
OL,14,FMs Oliver said: "The Government has
OL,15,Fpromised another national inquiry,
OL,16,Fthis time focused on so-called
OL,17,F'grooming gangs'.
OL,26,@tD@QOUtD@fO]vD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772447793
OL,3,CGrooming gang whistleblower taking
OL,4,CGovernment to court
OL,6,F"Survivors have every right to be
OL,7,Fheard, but why launch another inquiry
OL,8,Fwhen the recommendations of the last
OL,9,Fone remain unimplemented?
OL,11,F"After years of testimony and hundreds
OL,12,Fof millions of pounds spent, survivors
OL,13,Fshould not be asked to relive their
OL,14,Fmost traumatic experiences only to see
OL,15,Fno meaningful action follow.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772447793
OL,3,CGrooming gang whistleblower taking
OL,4,CGovernment to court
OL,6,F"Our charity has been deeply involved
OL,7,Fin the wider work to tackle child
OL,8,Fsexual abuse. I have long campaigned
OL,9,Ffor proper national data collection,
OL,10,Fincluding on the ethnicity of
OL,11,Fperpetrators, because without reliable
OL,12,Fevidence these crimes cannot be
OL,13,Fproperly understood or prevented.
OL,15,F"As a former police officer, I want
OL,16,Four agencies to have the tools to
OL,17,Feffectively combat child abuse. As a
OL,18,Fmother, I want children to be able to
OL,19,Fwalk the streets in safety.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772447793
OL,3,CGrooming gang whistleblower taking
OL,4,CGovernment to court
OL,6,F"Why does our Government have to be
OL,7,Fdragged to court to be forced to
OL,8,Fprotect children?"
OL,10,FThe hearing will consider whether the
OL,11,Fcharity's case should be allowed to
OL,12,Fproceed to a full judicial review
OL,13,Fhearing.
OL,15,FIf permission is granted, the charity
OL,16,Fsaid the Government will be required
OL,17,Fto explain its failure to implement
OL,18,Fthe child protection measures
OL,19,Frecommended by the IICSA.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772447793
OL,3,CGrooming gang whistleblower taking
OL,4,CGovernment to court
OL,6,FA government spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,Fgovernment is committed to tackling
OL,8,Fthe horrors of child sexual abuse and
OL,9,Fexploitation and getting justice for
OL,10,Fvictims and survivors. There can be
OL,11,Fnowhere for these evil perpetrators to
OL,12,Fhide.
OL,14,F"As part of this work we have set out
OL,15,Fa clear strategy for delivering
OL,16,FIICSA's recommendations, including the
OL,17,Fintroduction of legislation which is
OL,18,Fnow going through Parliament.
OL,26,@nD@aOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772447793
OL,3,CGrooming gang whistleblower taking
OL,4,CGovernment to court
OL,6,F"This includes introducing mandatory
OL,7,Freporting, reforming the disclosure
OL,8,Fand barring system, removing the three-
OL,9,Fyear limitation for victim personal
OL,10,Finjury claims, and making grooming a
OL,11,Fstatutory aggravating factor in
OL,12,Fsentencing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
